{{Quote|The Season Scepter?''"<br />"''Yes, a magical staff which controls the weather. We pass it to each other, causing the seasons to change.|[[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] and the Leaf Queen|<ref name="Season Scepter">{{Ewoks|The Season Scepter}}</ref>}}
[[File:SnowKingScepter-TSS.png|thumb|250px|The Snow King uses the season scepter.]]
The '''season scepter''' was a [[Magic/Legends|magical]] staff that controlled the seasons of the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. Four siblings&mdash;the [[Sun King]], the [[Leaf Queen]], the [[Snow King]], and the [[Flower Queen]]&mdash;rotated possession of the scepter. The season scepter had immense power, including the ability to create [[Water/Legends|snow]] and ice, change the [[Moon/Legends|moon's]] [[Temperature/Legends|temperature]], and propagate the growth of [[Flower/Legends|flowers]].<ref name="Season Scepter" />

